The use of psychic power requires great concentration.
While a psionicist is trained to be able to concentrate
even in the midst of combat, it still requires time.
Should the psionicist attempt to perform any action
during the power's concentration time (other than
normal melee combat), his concentration will be
interrupted, and the power will be aborted.  Be very
careful not to enter a command a few seconds too
early, or the power you were concentrating on will
be lost!
